  "markup": "Join Dr Christopher Carraway and members of the LTU team to review key topics and points from this years webinar series.\u0026nbsp; Topics to be included:\u003Cbr /\u003E\nReview relevant, \u0022Must Know\u0022 laser research published in 2014\u003Cbr /\u003E\nDiscuss the best \u0026ldquo;Methods\u0026rdquo; to treat pain and inflammation\u003Cbr /\u003E\nLearn how Priority Principle can be used to create endless protocols to treat every patient in your practice\u003Cbr /\u003E\nIntroduction of the Year-End Special from our laser sponsor\u003Cbr /\u003E\nAmple Interactive Q\u0026amp;A Time"
}]]></Value>
